Mistakes covered over in yellow or blacked out; some corrections in margins; significant syllables, words, or phrases highlighted in red throughout; vertical margins marked with triple red line.

msContents.summary: Medical text dealing with topics such as vomiting, purging tumors, deficiency of feces (purīṣakṣaya), etc., as well as cures and remedies for a variety of diseases.

msItem.title: Cikitsāmṛtasaṃgraha
चिकित्समृतसंग्रह
msItem.colophon: Colophon: iti cikitsāmṛtasaṃgrahe uttarakhaṃḍasamāptiḥ // śrīḥ // idaṃ pustakaṃ upādhyetapesmaśeḷaṃ prāṃtadaṃḍārājapurīkillejaṃjirā śrīhareśvaraśrīvardhananikaṭavastīprācīnaciregāṃvaśrī amṛteśvarapadīṃ madhye pāliśrīballālavināyakapadīṃ sāṃprataṃ avimuktavārāṇasīkāśīviśveśvarapadīṃ rāmaghāṭīṃ purohitopanāmabhābūbhiṣak baḍodekarākhya gṛhesvaparopakārārthaṃ likhitvā śubhaṃ pratiṣṭhitam asti // śake 1745 saṃvat 1880 āṣāṭaśuddhapaurṇamāsyāṃ tithau // (f. 257r)
